OL,6,GBBC regional TV and local radio
OL,7,Gservices have been affected by strike
OL,8,Gaction by members of the National Union
OL,9,Gof Journalists.
OL,11,FThe NUJ said it expected 900 staff to
OL,12,Fjoin the 24-hour walkout, which began
OL,13,Fat 11am today.
OL,15,FThe union says the BBC's plans to merge
OL,16,Fsome local radio programmes would
OL,17,F"undermine already hollowed out local
OL,18,Fradio content across England".
OL,20,FThe BBC said would try to minimise
OL,21,Fdisruption as much as possible.
OL,3,C24-hour NUJ strike affects BBC services
OL,4,Cin England
