OL,6,FThe proposals for more local radio
OL,7,Fstations to share programming would
OL,8,F"see no overall reduction in staffing
OL,9,Flevels or local funding" and deliver
OL,10,F"even greater value to communities", a
OL,11,FBBC spokesperson said.
OL,13,FOn TV, most English regions were unable
OL,14,Fto broadcast regional news programming
OL,15,Fat 1.30pm, 6.30pm and 10.30pm. In these
OL,16,Fregions, an edition of Planet Earth was
OL,17,Fshown at 1.30pm. Garden Rescue filled
OL,18,Fthe 6.30pm slot and at 10.30pm a
OL,19,Fsimulcast of the BBC News Channel was
OL,20,Fbroadcast (a Sportsday bulletin).
OL,3,C24-hour NUJ strike affects BBC services
OL,4,Cin England
