OL,6,FBBC South West managed to produce
OL,7,Flunchtime, early evening and
OL,8,Flate-evening editions of Spotlight on
OL,9,FWednesday. BBC East Midlands Today was
OL,10,Fbroadcast at 6.30pm and 10.30pm on
OL,11,FWednesday.
OL,13,FBBC East Midlands Today also went out
OL,14,Fon BBC One West Midlands at 10.30pm.
OL,16,FOn local radio, some stations broadcast
OL,17,Fa syndicated programme shortly after
OL,18,F11am. Others kept their own shows,
OL,19,Falthough many used stand-in hosts.
